### What I learned

I learned more about how to use flexbox and grid for amizing Layout.



```css
.flex-container {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
}

.grid-container{
  display: grid;
  grid-template-rows: repeat(3, 1fr);
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 2rem;
}
```

